title: Ishu bulauchhan sabailai
lyrics:
Yeshu bulauchhan sabailai -2
Prem sath bulauchhan angalomaa unko
'Yeshu bulauchhan sabailai -2
(A)
Hriday timro hatas bhayo, shanti cha tim laagi -2
Muktiko jyoti tim laagi, Ishu kaha linu aaja -2
(B)
Sab rog lai niko parne, shakti cha unai kaha -2
Muktiko jyoti tim laagi, pyar garnu sada timilai -2
